7.HTML and CSS
  Create a simple HTML page with a header that says "Welcome to My Website" and a paragraph of loreum ipsum text.Add some basic CSS to style the header with a blue color and center alignment.

/*HTML*/

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head> </head>
  <body>
    <h1 class="heading">Welcome to My Website</h1>
    <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet,consectetuer adipiscing elit.</p>
  </body>
</html>

/*CSS*/

.heading{
    color:blue;
    text-align: center;
}

8.JavaScript Basics 
  Write a JavaScript function `showAlert()` that displays an alert with the message "Hello, this is a JavaScript alert!".

let showAlert = () => {
    alert("Hello, this is a JavaScript alert!")
}

showAlert()









